- **End User**: End users of ambulatory healthcare IT solutions include hospitals, clinics, and ambulatory surgical centers, among others. Each end user segment has unique requirements for managing patient data, coordinating care, and ensuring regulatory compliance, driving the adoption of IT solutions in these settings.

